Personal_info.about: Hello, I'm Anil Chauhan! I am a Frontend Developer with a passion for creating user-friendly interfaces and developing scalable solutions. I have a strong foundation in web development technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Redux, Node.js, Git, and MUI. Additionally, I have experience in mobile app development with React Native. My focus is on delivering exceptional frontend experiences for web and mobile applications.
